insert into GREWordBook values ('473', 'comely', '[kʌmli]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=comely', '{adj.}++好看的；清秀的，秀丽的，标致的，漂亮的**++[古语]合适的，举止得体的**', '++Here, a comely woman coach jogs alongside an inmate in the prison yard.**++这儿，一个清秀的女子教练一起和犯人在监狱院子里慢跑。**++And there dwell in this comely garden white peacocks and peacocks that have blue breasts.**++在这秀美无比的花园里住着白孔雀和蓝胸孔雀。**++I am black, but comely, O ye daughters of Jerusalem, as the tents of Kedar, as the curtains of Solomon.**++耶路撒冷的众女子阿，我虽然黑，却是秀美，如同基达的帐棚，好像所罗门的幔子。**');
