insert into GREWordBook values ('475', 'commencement', '[kəmɛnsmənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commencement', '{n.}++开始(时间)；发端**++(学校等)毕业典礼；学位授予典礼**++典礼日；毕业日**', '++The commencement was held in the grand hall.**++毕业典礼在豪华的大厅举行。**++Plato was born in 427, which is four years after the commencement of the Peloponnesian War.**++柏拉图生于公元前，427，年，即伯罗奔尼萨战争,开始之后的四年。**++Not only has Harvard given me an extraordinary honour, but the weeks of fear and nausea I@ve experienced at the thought of giving this  commencement address have made me lose weight.**++这不仅因为哈佛给了我非比寻常的荣誉，而且为了这几个礼拜以来，由于想到这次毕业典礼演说而产生的恐惧与恶心让我减肥成功。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('476', 'commend', '[kəmɛnd]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commend', '{vt.}++推举，推荐，给…说好话：**++委托，把…交托给：**++称赞；表扬：**{vi.}++表扬；称赞**', '++I should like to commend this dictionary to you.**++我愿向你推荐这部词典。**++Tell him he’s good at his job, or commend his ability to provide for his family.**++告诉他，他对工作胜任有余，或是称赞他为家人创造高质量生活的能力。**++I commend UNITAID for taking the initiative to establish the Medicines Patent Pool.**++我对国际药品采购机制主动设立药物专利池表示称赞。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('477', 'commensurate', '[kəmɛnsərɪt, -ʃə-]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commensurate', '{adj.}++同量的；同大小的；同广阔的；同久远的**++相称的，相当的；适当的**++【数学】可公度的，有公度的；可通约的；有同量的**', '++Is it commensurate with the need and challenge that we face?**++与我们面临的需求和挑战是否相称？**++No. We deemed your level of speaking more commensurate with our data needs.**++我们认为你的语言水平与我们的数据需求更相称。**++Typically, a process@s privileges are commensurate with those of its owner.**++一般来说，进程的权限与其所有者的权限是相称的。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('478', 'commingle', '[kəmɪŋɡl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commingle', '{vt.}++使混合，掺和：**++合并(资金等)**', '++There has to be a way to commingle social preferences, economic performance, and long-term environmental goals.**++必须想办法综合考虑社会优先，经济运行和长远的环境目标。**++But it still seems to commingle sentiments of American exceptionalism with the idea of the universality of American values.**++但是它似乎仍然将美国例外论的思想情绪和普适的美国价值观混为一谈。**++Ground waters originating in different beds commingle.**++来源于不同层位的地下水相互混合。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('479', 'commiserate', '[kəmɪzəret]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commiserate', '{vt.}++同情，怜悯；哀悼：**++同情，怜悯；哀悼：**{vi.}++表示同情(或哀悼)；慰问(常与with连用)：**++表示同情(或哀悼)；慰问(常与with连用)：**{adj.}++表示同情(或怜悯、哀悼)的**', '++Sharing the lowlight of our day feels good because if we commiserate with our partner, we won@t feel so alone in our suffering.**++分享一天中的低潮是一件好事情，因为如果我们拥有配偶的同情，便会感到自己不再独自痛苦。**++Instead of yelling at the cashier after a long wait in line at the grocery store, commiserate with her about how hard such busy days can be on everyone.**++在杂货店排了很久的队之后，不要因为心里憋气就冲着收银员大喊大叫，而是要同情她的处境——人人都会经历这些忙碌的日子。**++Chat on the phone, go for a walk together or simply share a few laughs — or get together to commiserate about your cravings.**++打电话闲聊、一起散散步或就在一起笑笑—或聚一聚对你的吸烟欲望表示同情。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('480', 'commitment', '[kəmɪtmənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commitment', '{n.}++委托，托付；委任**++提付审议；提交**++拘留，监禁，收监，下狱，交押**++(精神病院的)收容，关进精神病院**++【法律】(法院颁发的)拘禁状；徒刑执行令**++犯罪**++(受)约束；(承担)义务；(作)保证**++许诺，诺言**++介入，牵连**++献身，投身**++登记在案的俱乐部会员资格**++对贿赂的权衡 [亦作 committal]**', '++But I do expect some commitment to reinforce coordination.**++但我认为会做出一些承诺以加强协调。**++To do this, we must have commitment at the highest level of government.**++要做到这一点，我们必须获得政府最高层的承诺。**++This principle is an extension of both the commitment principle and the success principle.**++这个原则是对承担义务原则和成功原则的一种扩展。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('481', 'committed', '[]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=committed', '{vt.}++commit的变形**{adj.}++承担义务的；忠于既定立场的，坚定的**++(政治上)有一定关系的，结盟的**{vt.}++把…托付给；托，委托；委任：**++付诸；藏于：**++监禁，把…交付看管；下狱；判处(徒刑等)：**++把…关进(精神病院)：**++使承担义务；使做出保证；许诺：**++干(坏事)；犯(罪)：**++指定…用于；调拨，调配…供使用：**++(把议程等)交付委员会**++提高：**{vi.}++[美国英语]保证，做出承诺：**++[美国英语]保证，做出承诺：**', '++He was perfectly sane when he committed the crime.**++他犯罪时，神志十分清醒。**++When a reporter asked the question, I said that, like a lot of couples, we’d had problems, but we were committed to each other and our marriage was strong.**++当一个记者问到私生活问题时，我说，与很多的夫妻一样，我和希拉里有过一些问题，但是我们都忠于对方，我们的婚姻非常牢固。**++What goals are you committed to and why?**++你的目标是什么？ 为什么有这样的目标？**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('482', 'commodious', '[kəmodɪəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commodious', '{adj.}++宽敞的，宽大的**++合适的，方便的**', '++Who wouldn’t want a job with a food salary and commodious living quarters?**++谁会不要一个薪水高、住房宽敞的工作呢？**++Designed as cruisers, many ketches are heavier, more stable in sea conditions, and more commodious down below.**++因为它们生来就是为了远行之用，因此它们通常更重，在各种海洋状况下更稳定， 船舱也更宽敞。**++“The Coffee houses particularly are very commodious for a free Conversation, and for reading at an easie Rate all manner of printed News,” noted one observer.**++一名观察家说，“尤其是咖啡馆，因其宽敞开阔的空间，很适合人们进行自由交谈，还可以舒舒服服的阅读各种新闻印刷品”。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('483', 'commonsensical', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commonsensical', '{adj.}', '++The commonsensical to do is to cut spending, but nobody wants to cut spending.**++减少开支才是符合常理的做法，但没人愿意这样做。**++That@s probably the most commonsensical way of putting the matter.**++想要表达的意思，这也许是阐述这一问题,最惯常的说法。**++Here is Lock@s theory of perception, its a very commonsensical one.**++这是洛克关于感知的理论，非常浅显易懂。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('484', 'commotion', '[kəmoʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=commotion', '{n.}++振动，动荡；激动；骚动**++骚扰；喧闹；混乱**++[古语]起义；暴乱；暴动**', '++Behind all of this commotion are day traders, those creatures of the dot-com era.**++在所有这些骚动背后的始作俑者，是那些来自网络时代的短线交易员。**++With the possible exception of the roller-derby in California, none will create as much commotion as the contest in Texas.**++除了加利福尼亚竞选可能性的例外，没有哪个州可以像得克萨斯州，创造出像竞选一样多的暴乱。**++Noticing the commotion, she reached into her purse for a handful of hard candies and offered them to the boys in return for their good behavior.**++的女士走进车厢坐了过来。 看到孩子们在骚动，她伸手从皮包里取出一把硬糖分发给两个孩子示意他们安分点。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('485', 'compatible', '[kəmpætəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=compatible', '{adj.}++和睦共处的，合得来的**++相容的**++协调的，和谐的，一致的**++(药物等)可配伍的**++【生物学】亲和的；可异花受精的，可嫁接的**++(电视机、计算机)兼容的**{n.}++(机器、电子文件等的)兼容**++【计算机】兼容机 [1994]**', '++If the column type and the data content are compatible, the data type is successfully altered.**++如果列类型和数据内容是兼容的，那么就能够成功更改数据类型。**++It can provide or require (or both) any interfaces, as long as they are compatible with any service ports that it is connected to.**++它能够提供或者要求（或者两者皆是）任何接口，只要它们同与其相连接的任何服务端口都兼容即可。**++Not all platforms are quite this compatible, though.**++不过并非所有的平台都是这样兼容的。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('486', 'compelling', '[kəmpɛlɪŋ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=compelling', '{vt.}++compel的变形**{adj.}++强迫性的，强制性的**++引人注目的；令人信服的**{vt.}++强迫，迫使，使不得不：**++以强力获得，强求，强取：**++[古语]使集合在一起，迫使联合**', '++Compelling ideas, to be sure, but we’d like to see evidence that any of this is possible.**++这确实是引人注目的想法，但是我们想看看这些任何这些想法可行的证据。**++Nearness has too much of the compelling about it and the imagination is not sufficiently free unless it can get away from its influence.**++与现实靠得太近，对感情有过分强迫的味道，而想象呢，除非它能摆脱感情的影响，不可能有充分的自由。**++But even with those tools, only you know whether or not you have the heart to execute on the opportunities we all recognize to launch a compelling new business.**++但是即使有了这些工具，也只有当你知道你是否有心来实现这些我们都认为可以建立一个引人注目的新企业的机会。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('487', 'compendium', '[kəmpɛndɪəm]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=compendium', '{n.}++摘要，概要；纲要；简编**++梗概，概论**++目录;清单 [亦作 compend]**', '++Read a compendium of published software architecture definitions.**++阅读已发布的软件架构定义的纲要。**++Eclipse automatically creates two Plug-In Development projects called org.osgi.compendium and cxf-dosgi-ri-singlebundle-distribution.**++Eclipse 会自动创建两个 Plug-In Development 项目，叫作 org.osgi.compendium 和 cxf-dosgi-ri-singlebundle-distribution。**++We will be consolidating all the feedback received in a compendium of events planned for World Health Day 2005, which will be accessible on the World Health Day 2005 web site.**++我们将汇总所有计划开展的2005年世界卫生日纪念活动的概要情况，这一信息将可以在2005年世界卫生日网站获取。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('488', 'complacency', '[kəmplesnsi]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=complacency', '{n.}', '++For now, though, its organising emotions are introspection and complacency.**++尽管就目前而言，其组织情绪是内向和自满。**++We have come a long way in this country, and we cannot allow complacency or naiveté to prevent us from finishing the journey.**++在我们这个国家，我们还有一段很长的路要走，我们不能允许自满或天真来阻止我们完成这段旅程。**++Yet all this betrays a dangerous complacency.**++然而，这种自满是非常危险的。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('489', 'complacent', '[kəmplesnt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=complacent', '{adj.}++心满意足的，洋洋自得的；满足的，自满的**++殷勤的；恳切的；讨好的**++不关心的**', '++I think this is positive, of great benefit, though some might see it as a threat and it does serve as a wake-up call for us not to become complacent.**++我认为这是正面的，有很大益处的，尽管也许有些人会把这看成是一种威胁而且它对我们的确也是一个警醒，让我们不要变得自满。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('490', 'complaisance', '[kəmplezns]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=complaisance', '{n.}++谦恭，殷勤，恳切，亲切；讨好**++恳切行为，讨好行为**', '++The tactile sensor applying PVDF as a sensitive material, has a complaisance surface and a minimal size, very suitable for the bionic hand.**++触滑觉组合传感器采用PVDF作为敏感材料，柔顺的传感器表面和小巧的尺寸使之能完全应用于仿生假手的手指上。**++Applying PVDF as a sensitive material, the developed sensor has a complaisance surface and a minimal size, very suitable for the bionical hand.**++传感器采用PVDF作为敏感材料，柔顺的传感器表面和小巧的尺寸使之能完全应用于仿生假手的手指上。**++All teachers shall respect students and treat them with complaisance, insist on self-discipline and self-love for friendship with students, and make full efforts to spread traditional Chinese culture.**++尊重学员，儒雅待人，自律自爱，建立师生友情，努力做一名中华文化交流使者。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('491', 'complementary', '[kɑmpləmɛntri]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=complementary', '{adj.}++补足的，补充的**++互补的，互为补充的；互补作用的；【遗传学】互补的**++【医学】(治疗等)互补性的；非正统的；自然疗法的；(医师)非正统的**++非主流的，另类的[1997]**{n.}++补充物，补足物**++【物理学】互补色(=complementary colour)**', '++That would be good for my apprentice to have, complementary.**++补充说一下，那会是成为我徒弟的优势。**++The readings you should think of as complementary to my lectures.**++因为你应该把那些书当作是我讲座的补充。**++If you have done your research and wish to try a complementary therapy, the next step is to talk to your personal doctor or HIV specialist.**++如果在经过研究后您仍然希望尝试补充疗法，那么您下一步要做的就是与您的私人医生或HIV病毒专家谈一谈。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('492', 'compliant', '[kəmplaɪənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=compliant', '{adj.}', '++They’ll grow up skilled and compliant but without the audacity to be great.**++她们长大后有技能又顺从，却会因缺乏无畏精神而成不了大器。**++At the root of the issue are compliant shareholders that rarely stand up to management.**++问题的根本原因是顺从的股东很少站起来挑战管理层。**++Additionally, some of the CSS tests listed on MSDN are inaccurate, and browsers that actually pass these tests are not compliant with the standard.**++此外，MSDN上列出的CSS测试很不精确，事实上，完全通过了这些测试的浏览器并不与标准兼容。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('493', 'complicate', '[kɑmplɪket]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=complicate', '{vt.}++使复杂化，把…弄复杂；使…变得更糟；使陷入：**++使复杂化，把…弄复杂；使…变得更糟；使陷入：**{adj.}++【昆虫学】(昆虫翅膀)纵折的**++【植物学】(某些植物的叶子)折叠的**++[古语]复杂的，麻烦的**', '++If the answer to all of these questions is no, a framework will only complicate matters.**++如果所有这些问题的答案都为否，那么使用框架只会把事情变复杂。**++The selection service is one of the more difficult services to implement correctly because it has some valuable features that complicate the implementation.**++选择服务是比较难以正确实现的服务之一，因为它具有一些使实现复杂化的有价值的功能。**++The differences in command line tools, output formats, values, and other information all complicate what should otherwise be a simple process.**++命令行工具、输出格式、值和其他信息之间的差异全都会使原本应该简单的过程变得复杂化。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('494', 'compliment', '[kɑːmplɪmənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=compliment', '{n.}++恭维话，赞美辞，颂辞**++谦恭有礼，敬意**++[复数]致敬，问候；祝贺**++[古语]谢礼，慰劳品；赏金，小账**{vt.}++祝贺，向…致贺辞；向…致意，问候；赞美；恭维：**++向(某人)敬赠礼物，送礼以表敬意**', '++Compliment them, and show respect.**++恭维他们，表现敬意。**++If you grew up with harsh criticism and ridicule and impatience, then be sure to compliment, love, and exercise patience with your children.**++如果你在苛刻的批评，嘲笑和焦躁下成长，请确保一定要称赞，疼爱并且寻来耐心地对待你的孩子。**++Whenever my girlfriend comes back from the salon, I always compliment her hair.**++我女友每次从美容院回来，我都会称赞她的头发。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('495', 'comply', '[kəmplaɪ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=comply', '{vi.}++依从，顺从，服从；遵守；应允，同意(常与with连用)：**++[废语]讲究繁文缛节**', '++Visitors to the mine must comply with the rules.**++到矿上参观的人必须遵守规章。**++It is your choice as to whether you choose to comply.**++选择是否遵守这些法律取决于您自己的决定。**++If we reinforce the traffic security education and more people comply with traffic regulations, I believe one day traffic accidents can be avoided.**++如果我们加强交通安全教育，更多的人遵守交通规则，我相信总有一天交通事故是可以避免的。**');
