insert into GREWordBook values ('1513', 'intercessor', '[,ɪntɚsɛsɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=intercessor', '{n.}++调解者；说情者**++【宗教】代理主教**', '++Catholics pray to Mary as an intercessor.**++天主教徒向玛利亚祈祷，并把她看作仲裁者。**++An intercessor is one who pleads on behalf of someone else, for example a lawyer who speaks in a law court on behalf of his client.**++代求者的工作，就是代表另一人辩护和求情，就如律师在法庭上代表当事人申诉一样。**++In opposition to the rational approach to divine understanding that the schoolmen adopted, Bernard preached an immediate faith, in which the intercessor was the Virgin Mary.**++反对理性的方法去接近和理解神，就像经院采纳的。本笃鼓吹一种直接的信仰，调解人是圣母玛利亚。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('1514', 'interdict', '[ɪntɚdɪkt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=interdict', '{vt.}++(以禁令)禁止；制止：**++【军事】(以炮火等)封锁；阻断**++【天主教】停止…的圣事活动(或教权)**{n.}++【民法】(法庭等作出的)禁令；强制**++【历史】(古罗马执政官发布的)禁制令；获取禁制令的程序**++(由于精神病等原因)不能自行其是者；受监护者**++【天主教】停止教权；停止参加圣事活动**', '++In the first half of 2009, the army special forces company I was with repeatedly try to interdict Taliban.**++009年的上半年，我跟随着一个特种部队,我们屡次想要阻断塔利班分子。**++With Mexico, in addition to trade cooperation, we are working together to identify and interdict threats at the earliest opportunity, even before they reach North America.**++除了与墨西哥的经贸合作，我们正在共同努力以确保尽快的识别并制止威胁，甚至在威胁到达北美之前。**++Caption :The troops in Helmand will also seek to interdict opium shipments and persuade local farmers to plant alternative crops, such as wheat.**++描述：进入赫尔曼德省的美军试图阻断当地的鸦片运输线，并劝说当地农民改种粮食作物，比如小麦。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('1515', 'interim', '[ɪntərɪm]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=interim', '{n.}++间歇；中间时期；过渡时期；其间**{adj.}++间歇的；过渡期间的**++暂时的；临时的**{n.}', '++Please give me an interim receipt.**++请给我一张临时的收据。**++These customizations can be just about anything you need, but in this case we will focus on installing interim fixes into the virtual machine instance.**++这些定制可以是您所需的任何内容，但是本例中，我们将主要关注将临时补丁安装到虚拟机实例中。**++In fact you can also define interim levels of maturity: what is the next major maturity goal, defining roadmaps to attain each of these goals with clear business value.**++实际上，您还可以定义临时的成熟度级别：下一个主要成熟度目标是什么，定义路线图以实现这些目标（具有明确的商业价值）。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('1516', 'interlock', '[ɪntɚlɑk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=interlock', '{vt.}++使联结；使连锁：**++使联结；使连锁：**{vi.}++联结；连锁：**++联结；连锁：**{n.}++联结；连锁**++连锁装置[亦作 ignition interlock]**++【纺织业】**++双罗纹针织物；棉手布**++用双罗纹针织品制造的衣服**{adj.}++连锁的**', '++Notice how the original jawbones interlock to form sturdy walls.**++请注意下颚骨是如何联锁而形成坚墙的。**++Behaviors interlock in a way that rewards fairness and punishes its violation, Henrich said.**++亨里奇说。 人类行为以连锁反应的方式，奖励公平，惩罚违规。**++An alcolock, or more formally a “breath alcohol ignition interlock device” (BAIID), is fitted to a car’s ignition to stop a driver from starting it if he’s over the drink-driving limit.**++酒精锁，正式名称为“酒精气敏点火自锁装置”，是安装在汽车的点火装置内以阻止驾车人在酒精浓度超过安全标准时启动汽车的装置。**');
