insert into GREWordBook values ('1662', 'madcap', '[mædkæp]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=madcap', '{n.}++极易冲动的人(尤指少女)；狂妄的人；行为鲁莽的人**{adj.}++极为冲动的，鲁莽的，轻率的**', '++But the role of madcap spiritual godmother to little misfit monsters everywhere is one that Lady Gaga already has down cold.**++但是作为随处可见的小怪兽们鲁莽的教母，这个角色的特性Lady Gaga早已具备。**++Everyone mocked Libya’s madcap “Leader,” but loved his money even more.**++人人嘲笑利比亚卤莽的“领导人”，人人都更爱他的金钱。**');
