insert into GREWordBook values ('1986', 'perceptible', '[pɚsɛptəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perceptible', '{adj.}', '++The next, there seem to be small but perceptible policy shifts towards each other.**++下一分钟，双方却在向对方靠拢；政策变化虽然微小，但是却明晰可辨。**++In addition to the physical body you dwell in, you are also a compilation of energy, partly perceptible and partly imperceptible.**++除了你所居住的肉体之外，你也是一个能量的汇集，部分可感知部分不可感知。**++Speaking for myself, one of the reasons I feel this so strongly is the fact that the fiction I write is itself undergoing a perceptible transformation.**++说到我自己，令我感到这一点的其中一个缘由就是，我写的故事本身正经历着可以感觉得到的转换。**');
