insert into GREWordBook values ('2046', 'pivotal', '[pɪvətl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pivotal', '{adj.}++枢轴的；中枢的；心轴的**++枢要的；起轴心作用的；关键性的**{n.}++关键事物；中心事物**', '++I speak openly as I realize that all these challenges and issues affect the pivotal role of the United Nations, its credibility and its existence.**++我之所以开诚布公地这样说，只是因为我认识到，所有这些挑战和问题都影响到本组织的关键作用、其信誉乃至存在。**++The management team plays the pivotal role in developing and reinforcing these skills through daily guidance and continuous hands-on coaching and feedback.**++管理团队通过日常指导和持续的实际辅导以及反馈在开发和增强这些技巧方面扮演着枢轴的角色。**++The code in Listing 2 highlights the pivotal functionality of that rule.**++列表 2 中的代码强调了这一规则的关键功能。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2047', 'placate', '[pleket]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=placate', '{vt.}{n.}', '++I tried to placate her by offering to pay for the repairs.**++我提出支付修理费来抚慰他。**++The minister@s cronies have an election coming up, and the best way to placate voters is to promise them land.**++部长的密友马上要参加大选了，抚慰选民最好的方法就是向他们保证可以得到土地。**++But even though the military is widely popular with the public, there was no sign that the government shakeup would placate protesters, who added anti-Suleiman slogans to their demands.**++尽管军队在公众中大受欢迎，然而并没有迹象表明政府的调整能够抚慰已经将反对苏雷曼的口号加入他们要求中的抗议者。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2048', 'placebo', '[pləsibo]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=placebo', '{n.}++【天主教】为死者唱的晚祷词(丧歌)**++安慰剂(指无药效、仅产生心理作用的制剂)**++安慰物；宽慰话**', '++Instead, we see the effects of treatment plus placebo effects that are shaped by the subjects’ expectations.**++反而我们看到的是加上人们对治疗本身的期望之后即安慰剂效应的治疗的效果。**++Or it could be that the needles caused a “super placebo” effect, triggering a real reaction in the brain that changes the way the body perceives and responds to pain.**++或者是因为针灸造成了一种“超级安慰剂”效应，并触发了大脑内的一个反应，这种反应能改变身体对疼痛信号的感知和回应。**++I went to the labs of the leading placebo researchers in Turin and subjected myself to some experimentation.**++我去了在都灵一些安慰剂主要研究人员的实验室，并亲身经受了一些实验。**');
