insert into GREWordBook values ('2156', 'prolix', '[prolɪks]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=prolix', '{adj.}++令人生厌的；啰唆的**++冗长的；好长篇大论的**', '++As a result of the scattered structure, the drama is so prolix that the mythos has to be weakened;**++结构松散，导致全剧篇幅过长，冲淡了戏剧的主题；**++Then for complicated sine integral and prolix formulae, the study on symmetrical dipole can be easily solved by MATLAB.**++对于复杂的正弦积分和冗长的公式，都可以通过简单的编程实现仿真。**++Prithee , darlingmost! - court me rather than the peevish prolix.**++我请求你， 我的最爱！ 追求我，毋宁倔强的冗说。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2157', 'prologue', '[prolɔɡ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=prologue', '{n.}++序言；序诗；(戏剧的)开场白；(尤指正戏开始前由主要角色朗诵的)诗白**++作开场白的演员**++序幕性事件；序幕**{vt.}++为…作序(或序诗)：**++为(戏剧)念开场白**++成了…的开端 [亦作prolog]**', '++In the prologue, the first thing you do is save the link register.**++在序言中，所要做的第一件事情是保存链接寄存器。**++McCartney contributes a prologue to the book, in which he explains, "We were looking for something different.**++麦卡特尼在本书的序言中解释说，“我们正寻求一些与以往不同的尝试。**++Jesus comes into the cosmos,so the cosmos as a dark enemy place in which Jesus invades it in a sense is one of the major themes of the Gospels that you get right here in the prologue.**++耶稣来到宇宙中，宇宙是个黑暗而充满敌意的地方,从某种意义上说，耶稣侵入了宇宙,这是你能从序言读到的,这本福音的主题之一。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2158', 'prolong', '[prəlɑːŋ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=prolong', '{vt.}++延长；拉长；拖长；延长时间；使持久：**++拖长(音节等的)发音：**++[废语]推迟 [亦作prolonggate]**', '++What factors shorten, prolong or amplify the effect of deception?**++什么因素会缩短、延长或扩张欺骗的结果？**++We know what to do to prevent infections and save or prolong lives.**++我们知道该怎么去做，来预防感染并且拯救或者延长生命。**++But this new era must not repeat or prolong the mistakes of its predecessor.**++但是这个新纪元必须不能重复或延长其前任的错误。**');
