insert into GREWordBook values ('2393', 'rickety', '[rɪkəti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=rickety', '{adj.}++佝偻病的；患佝偻病的；似佝偻病的**++摇晃的；蹒跚的**++易倒的；易垮的；不稳固的；不结实的**', '++The chair is a bit rickety [shaky].**++这椅子有点摇晃。**++I saw him padlock the rickety door behind us.**++我见他在我们背后把摇摇晃晃的门锁上了。**++Practice session over, we make our way down to the beach, finishing our journey down to the shore with a rickety ladder and rope.**++练习结束，我们艰难地下到海滩，完成了利用摇晃的梯子和绳子下到海滨的旅程。**');
