insert into GREWordBook values ('2403', 'rive', '[raɪv]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=rive', '{vt.}++撕碎；扯破；劈开；使破裂：**++扯下;拉下(常与away,from,off连用)：**++使(心)破碎，使伤心；使悲痛：**{vi.}++撕开；裂开；破裂：**++撕开；裂开；破裂：**{n.}++[英国方言]**++扯；拉**++裂口；裂缝**', '++To reduce the high up-front costs for customers, Rive will lease homeowners the panels at a rate based on the size of their system.**++为了替消费者减少前期费用，赖夫根据安装系统的大小，按一定比率收取太阳能面板的租赁费用。**++By saving "pennies here and pennies there, " he says, and increasing the volume of installations, Rive is driving down the costs of solar power.**++赖夫说，本着这里省一点，那里省一点，增加安装容量的原则，公司正在降低太阳能发电的成本。**++Lyndon Rive, solar@s master salesman, wants to know.**++林登·赖夫，太阳能专业销售商，想知道这个答案。**');
