insert into GREWordBook values ('2586', 'sober', '[sobɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sober', '{adj.}++未饮醉的，清醒的**++适度的；有节制的**++镇静的，冷静的**++严肃的，庄重的，庄严的**++持重的，稳重的**++不言过其实的，不夸大的**++(颜色)素的，暗淡的；(服装)朴素的**++能自我克制的，有自制力的**++有理智的，合理的**++[古语] 从容不迫的，不慌不忙的**{vt.}++使清醒；使醒酒 (up):**++[口语] 使冷静；使自制；使严肃 (down):**{vi.}++清醒起来；醒酒 (off， up):**++[口语] 变得冷静；变得严肃 (down):**', '++These bloody lessons would sober most people down.**++这些血的教训总会令大多数人清醒了吧。**++The lessons learned at the cost of blood helped to sober us.**++血的教训使我们的头脑清醒了。**++For us there is no reality nor for you either you sober locks.**++对我们而言，不存在现实，对你,或者对你清醒的锁。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2587', 'sodden', '[sɑdn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sodden', '{adj.}++湿润的；湿透的**++(食物)未熟的，黏糊糊的**++湿漉漉的**++无表情的，呆滞的，(头脑)迟钝的**++麻木的，无精打采的**++(脸部等)肿胀的**++[古语] 煮沸的，烧开的**{vt.}++使浸湿；使湿透：**++使变得呆滞，使变得麻木：**{vi.}++被浸湿；湿透：**++[废语、古语] seethe 的过去分词**', '++It was in Burma, a sodden morning of the rains.**++绞  刑  那是在缅甸，一个泡在雨水中的清晨。**++Through one of the broken panes I heard the rain impinge upon the earth, the fine incessant needles of water playing in the sodden beds.**++透过一块破碎的窗玻璃，传来了雨水着地的声响。 连绵的细雨犹如行行绣针，洒向湿透的花圃。**++Forty rooms file off it, some of them so damp that they are filled today with stalagmites and stalactites formed by calcium dripping from the sodden concrete.**++四十个房间一字排开，一部分房间非常潮湿，长满了石笋和钟乳石，它们是湿透的混凝土滴下的钙凝结成的。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2588', 'solace', '[]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solace', '{n.}++安慰，慰藉**++安慰物；起安慰作用的事物[亦作 solacement]**{vt.}++安慰，使快乐；使平静：**++减轻；缓和：**++[古语] 使(住所)舒适**++[废语] 为…提供娱乐**{vi.}++[废语] 安慰，抚慰；起安慰作用**', '++Above all, it requires clairvoyant souls—that is, without solace.**++而且，它需要无需慰藉的洞察力的灵魂。**++My wife would be widowed and my children orphaned, but they would take solace in the knowledge that I had given my life to a cause that the people of some nation believed in.**++我的老婆会成为寡妇，我的孩子们会成为孤儿，但是她们会得到几许安慰于此：我所献身的事业是一些国家的人们深信不疑的伟大事业。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2589', 'solder', '[sɑdɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solder', '{n.}++用以焊接的合金，(低温)焊料**++接合物；连接因素**{vt.}++焊，焊接，焊合：**++使连在一起，使联合：**++修补：**{vi.}++焊，焊接，焊合：**++联结，连在一起**', '++This superior reliability comes from advances in packaging techniques and epitaxial structure, together with the use of hard solder construction.**++这种超级可靠性来自于封装技术和外延结构的发展，也得益于硬焊接架构的使用。**++But, no matter how simplistic this design is, you will still have to solder copper pipe joints if you want to tap into your existing hot water system.**++但是，这个设计无论多么简单，你总得要焊接铜管，以便接入你现有的热水供应系统。**++Each sculptural planter is made-to-order with handmade glass and lead-free solder and comes with everything you need but the plants.**++每个艺术花盆都是定制的。 它们由手工制作的玻璃和无铅焊料接合而成，交付使用时，万事俱备，只欠花卉。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2590', 'solemnity', '[səlɛmnəti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solemnity', '{n.}++严肃；庄重；郑重**++庄严，隆重**++[常用复数] 庄重的仪式**++【法律】必要形式**', '++Taken together, Han is telling his readersthat solemnity and seniority are not to be trusted.**++总而言之，韩寒在告诉他的读者，庄严之物和年资都不足凭信。**++Like me my dad disliked having his picture taken and in most pictures affects a sort of Teutonic solemnity.**++就像我一样，我的父亲并不喜欢拍照，而且在大多数的照片中有一种日耳曼人的严肃。**++Having a Starbucks in the Forbidden City, he wrote on his blog, "undermines the Forbidden City@s solemnity" and is "an insult to Chinese civilisation".**++故宫里有星巴克，他在博客写道，“破坏了紫禁城的庄严肃穆，”并且是“对中国文明的侮辱”。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2591', 'solicitous', '[səlɪsɪtəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solicitous', '{adj.}++焦虑的，担心的，挂念的，关心的 (about， for)**++渴望的；热切的**++细心的**++非常注意的，十分讲究的**', '++William seems particularly solicitous and engrossed in looking after his wife, focusing on what he’s doing.**++威廉看起来也显得特别殷勤，全神贯注地看着他的妻子，专注于自己正在做的事情。**++Picture an encounter between two people who both intend to create a harmonious relationship, but one perceives the other@s solicitous, polite--even generous--behavior as imposing.**++想象两个都打算创造和谐的关系人相遇，但其中一人感觉对方的挂念、礼貌、慷慨是一种强加行为。**++But a good lover is always solicitous of their beloved’s pleasure, and ensures their partner takes as much from the boudoir as they do themselves.**++不过，好的情侣总是关心他们的爱人是否满足，并确保他们的伴侣同样享受这个过程。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2592', 'solid', '[sɑlɪd]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solid', '{adj.}++立体的；立方体的**++固体的；固态的**++实心的；非中空的**++坚实的**++牢固的，结实的；坚硬的**++实在的，不浅薄的；严肃认真的**++货真价实的；纯质的；纯色的；纯一的**++质密的；浓密的**++紧密相连的，连成一片的**++彻底的；完全的；真正的**++充分的；确实的，有根据的**++可信赖的；体面的，可敬的**++连续的，不停顿的**++整整的，完整的**++连写的，不用连字符的**++真正的**++头脑冷静的，理智的**++资金雄厚的；殷实的**++丰盛的**++重大的**++结实的，有力的**++(意见等)完全一致的**++密切联合的，紧密团结的**++[口语] [in solid] 关系友好的**++[美国俚语](尤指音乐)精彩的，一流的，绝佳的**++【数学】立方的；三次(方)的**++【印刷】(行间)密排的，不用铝条隔开的**++【航天学、航空学】用固体燃料的**{n.}++立体；立方体**++固体**++[用复数] (液体中的)固态物，固体物**++[用复数] 固体食物，非流质食物**{adv.}++连续地，不间断地**++全部地，完全地**++[美国口语] 无疑，肯定**', '++The solid particles were filtered from the solution.**++固体颗粒从溶液中过滤出来。**++My theory is established on the solid basis of facts.**++我的理论是以可靠的事实作为根据的。**++All substances, whether they are gaseous, liquid or solid, are made of atoms.**++一切物质，不论它们是气体、液体还是固体， 都是由原子构成的。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2593', 'soliloquy', '[səlɪləkwi]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=soliloquy', '{n.}++自言自语**++(小说等人物中的)独白 **++【戏剧】独白**', '++We see him trying out for an amateur company by doing Richard III@s "winter of our discontent" soliloquy.**++我们看到他试图为一个业余的喜剧公司表演理查德三世“烦恼的冬天”的独白。**++On the screen, a shadow flickered—a shadow with feet like boxcars and a smile like the last soliloquy of Hamlet. He was a tenderfoot.**++在萤幕上，一个影子跳动着——这个影子脚上穿着硕大的鞋子，脸上有着仿佛哈姆雷特在最后独白时的诡异笑容。**++No one@s giving a long soliloquy in this situation -- or if they are, they@re a very strange duck, which would actually give you a lot of material to work with.**++一个人长段地独白似乎不现实——或如果是这样，他们就非常的奇怪了，而这样实际上正给了你很多创作的材料。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2594', 'solitude', '[sɑlətud]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solitude', '{n.}++孤独；隐居**++寂寞**++偏僻，荒凉；偏僻(或荒凉)的地方**', '++Only nature and solitude.**++只有自然和孤独。**++She will want nothing but solitude and you.**++除了孤独和你，她将别无所求。**++One surprising answer, in this age of alienation, is a lack of solitude.**++在这个疏远的时代，一个令人惊讶的答案就是“缺乏必要的孤独”。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2595', 'solvent', '[sɑlvənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=solvent', '{adj.}++有偿付能力的；无债务的**++有溶解力的**++起削弱作用的，起瓦解作用的**{n.}++溶剂，溶媒**++解决方法；可说明的事物；解答**++起削弱(或瓦解)作用的事物**', '++I have moles of solvent.**++只有溶剂的摩尔数。**++So this constant here cares what the solvent is.**++所以这个常数与溶剂是什么有关。**++Some of everything is in our water because water is also the universal solvent.**++由于水是地球上最广泛的溶剂，地球上很大一部分都在这里面。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2596', 'somatic', '[somætɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=somatic', '{adj.}++【解剖学、动物学】体腔的；体腔壁的**++【细胞生物学】体细胞的；作用于体细胞的**++身体的，躯体的；肉体的**++细胞体的；体浆的，躯质的**', '++Such experiences ex-somatic, which the dreamer feels to be out of his physical body, are called lucid dreams.**++这种经验超脱于肉体，做梦者感觉到自己在脱离他的身体，这被称为清醒梦。**++To balance on a bike we need somatic tacit knowledge, but to ride it in traffic we need collective tacit knowledge.**++为了在自行车上取得平衡，我们需要躯体隐性知识，此外为了在车流中骑行，我们还需要集体隐性知识。**++I call this, cat-like, brain-and-body kind of tacit knowledge "somatic tacit knowledge": it is knowledge stored in the muscles, nerve pathways, and synaptic connections.**++我称之为类猫化脑体型隐性知识，即“躯体隐性知识”：它是存储于肌肉、神经通路以及突触连接中的知识。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2597', 'somber', '[sɑːmbər]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=somber', '{adj.}', '++It was a fun movie, but the ending was rather somber.**++这是一部有趣的电影，不过结局有点沉闷。**++But on this particular call, he was somber, quiet, and sad.**++但就这个电话而言，他是那么的安静、伤心、闷闷不乐。**++Look at Berlin, where the bullet holes in the buildings and the somber stones and pillars near the Brandenburg Gate insist that we never forget our common humanity.**++看看柏林吧，在这里，建筑物上密布的弹孔和勃兰登堡门附近阴森的石头和柱子时刻提醒我们，永远不要忘记我们共同的人性。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2598', 'somnolence', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=somnolence', '{n.}++瞌睡，困倦，昏昏欲睡**++嗜睡;嗜睡状态[亦作 somnolency]**', '++The most common side effect was insomnia, somnolence, and drowsiness, which occurred in 1,028 (2.6 percent) patients.**++最常见的副作用就是失眠和失去睡意，其中有1028（2.6%）个病人出现过。**++Karen occasionally talked in her sleep, muttering and mumbling, no words that he could decipher, the language of somnolence.**++卡伦有时会说梦话，嘟嘟囔囔的，亨利一个词也听不出：梦之国的语言。**++You should know o arjuna that the mode of ignorance as the cause of delusion enslaving all embodied beings born of nescience ; by negligence listlessness and somnolence.**++你应该知道，阿诸那啊，无知是一切妄想的根源，它因疏忽，冷漠和困倦而奴役，束缚了所有天生无知的被肉体包裹的灵魂。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2599', 'sonnet', '[sɑnɪt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sonnet', '{n.}++十四行诗**{vi.}++写作十四行诗**{vt.}++为…作十四行诗，用十四行诗歌颂**', '++This last line of Edwin Arlington Robinson@s sonnet “Credo” expresses the general basis of my belief.**++阿林顿。 罗宾逊的十四行诗《信条》中的最后一行，概括了我的基本信仰。**++It@s in recognition of what we can think of as this time- honored historical irony that Milton writes such a memorable line, a wonderful line, in his sonnet on the new Presbyterian regime.**++这刚好跟我们这次所想的相应-,这个令人尊敬的历史性讽刺，弥尔顿写得如此有纪念意义，如此绝妙，在十四行诗里，他所写的新长老派的政体。**++I@ve been doing this for many years, and all of a sudden comes a sonnet.**++我在这方面做了很多年，所有的一切就像一首十四行诗。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2600', 'soothe', '[sʊð]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=soothe', '{vt.}++使平静，使镇定；安抚，安慰：**++减轻，缓和(疼痛、痛苦、怀疑等)：**++[古语] 奉承，迎合**++[古语] 用许诺哄骗**{vi.}++起抚慰作用；起镇定作用**{n.}++[罕用语]**++安慰感**++镇定作用**', '++But the release, apparently, was not enough to soothe China’s fury.**++但是很明显释放中国船长并不足以缓和中国的愤怒。**++And yet I never stopped loving him and using his love like a battery booster whenever I needed to rev up my courage or soothe my sagging spirit.**++但是，我对他的爱从未停止过。 而他的爱更是我的充电器，在我需要勇气或是意志消沉的时候给我鼓励和安慰。**++Actually there is no necessary relation between loneliness and lover. Some people just use it as an excuse to soothe themselves after the failure of love.**++你是否找恋人跟你现在是否寂寞这根本就不着边际，只不过是有些人在恋爱失败之后的一个借口，用来安慰自己的借口。**');
insert into GREWordBook values ('2601', 'sop', '[sɑp]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sop', '{n.}++(泡在牛奶、羹汤等里面的)面包片；湿软食品**++湿透了的人(或东西)**++(液体等的)一滩**++小贿赂；礼品，抚慰器**++[口语] 懦夫；笨蛋；窝囊废**{vt.}++在(汤)里浸(或泡)：**++使浸泡，使湿透：**++吸收(水分、液体等)(常与 up连用)：**++向…行贿；向…送礼求情(或抚慰)**{vi.}++湿透：**++渗透(常与 in 连用)：**{abbr.}++standard operating procedure 标准操作规程**++standing operating procedure 【军事】标准作战规定**{abbr.}', '++For details on how to correlate the events that SOP generates, watch for Part 8 of this series.**++对于如何将 SOP 生成的事件相关联的详细信息，请注意该系列文章的第 8 部分。**++With SOP in place, you can rest assured that whatever you view was sent by the expected origin; there cannot be any code from other (possibly suspect) origins.**++如果有了 SOP，就可以确保您查看的所有内容都是由预期的源发送的；不可能存在来自其他（可能是可疑的）源的代码。**++Eliminating the SOP would be great for phishers because you might look at a valid page from a trusted Web site, but a third party can monitor your actions and any data you send or receive.**++消除 SOP 对于网页假冒者无疑是个好消息，因为您虽然浏览的是一个来自可信站点的有效页面，但是第三方却有可能监视您的行动以及任何您所发送或接收的数据。**');
