insert into GREWordBook values ('2666', 'stipulate', '[stɪpjulet]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=stipulate', '{vt.}++规定，约定，订明：**++坚持把…作为协议的条件：**++保证，确保：**{vi.}++规定；讲定，约定(for)：**++[废语]订契约；讲条件**{adj.}', '++Can you stipulate they would carry out the treaty?**++你能保证他们会执行该条约吗?**++The contract would stipulate reimbursements at any point the engagement is called off.**++该协议将规定在任何时间段取消婚约应支付的赔偿。**++If not, he said, it should stipulate having the self-defense forces as a military capability.**++他说，如果不废除，就应规定把自卫队当作一种军事能力而保有。**');
